滲透。如今在香港和台灣的港獨台獨危局就是我們付出的慘重代價。<br />\n回复<br />\n&ntilde;3<br />\n今天 12:11<br />\nZerenman<br />\nZerenman：老胡關心關心股市吧，機構報團炒作白酒，白酒價格都上了天，也沒人管，難道真的喝酒強國嗎，而反觀科技股有一點點漲幅，就要打壓，<br />\n回复<br />\n&ntilde;4<br />\n今天 11:33<br />\n哈嘛秘籍<br />\n哈嘛秘籍：中肯<br />\n回复<br />\n&ntilde;1<br />\n今天 10:58<br />\n柒海<br />\n柒海：憋屈就憋屈嘛！老二被老大打壓，憋屈不挺正常嗎？大家都能理解，有啥不能承認的[攤手][攤手]過些年，等咱當老大了，就不憋屈了！ ！<br />\n回复<br />\n&ntilde;2<br />\n今天 10:56"},{"pid":"680a8a3218d3305345f13eefd02a84a25bc3e537","tid":2292233,"uid":74442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:45:20.000Z","msg":"袁木最誠實"},{"pid":"e7b7668f9df1175ef7c08385dcabdfbb105c2799","tid":2292233,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:45:52.000Z","msg":"如果元朝都係你自古以來<br />\n你d土地去到歐洲喎"},{"pid":"f42573427a018ffc65e486d658c6b8b472b773d2","tid":2292233,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:47:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">文有老胡，武有馬保國，復興指日可待</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb4e6b5645b54439b9b209e589c1167640561f5","tid":2292233,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1076efc1013645148574304b0874be24ebe4b3a2","tid":2292233,"uid":29880,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VcGZ6zM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVcGZ6zM.jpg&h=9ae56ee4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n丟整塊"},{"pid":"bb8244cbb73b9115a9798876ea33733e1e9628f1","tid":2292233,"uid":53601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:47:49.000Z","msg":"海參威是中國最後一塊拼圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f818b813e19188e7a2c55b13c92be043eec3dd00","ti